M810 (kill‑ring status)

void gcode_M810(void)
{
    uint8_t active = kill_triggered();
    report_message(active ? "KILL-RING: TRIGGERED" : "KILL-RING: OK");
}

Add to your G‑code dispatch table:
case 810:
    gcode_M810();
    break;

Now you can test the ring anytime:
M810

Output:

KILL-RING: OK

or:

KILL-RING: TRIGGERED
